  "privacyPolicyTitle": "الخصوصية Policy",
  "privacyLastUpdated": "Last updated: March 2025",
  "privacyIntro": "At {appName}, your الخصوصية is paramount. This الخصوصية Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal and health-related data. By using our services, you agree to the practices described below.",
  "privacySectionDataCollection": "1. Data Collection",
  "privacyDataCollectionBody": "We collect the following categories of data: • Personal Information: Nالاسم البريد الإلكتروني address, الهاتف number, التاريخ of birth, and gender. • الصحة Data: Blood type, aالحساسية chronic conditions, mالأدوية vital signs, symptom logs, and الفرز results. • طوارئ Contacts: Names, الهاتف numbers, and relationships of your designated contacts. • Device Data: Device type, operating system, and app version for compatibility and sالدعم • Usage Data: Feature interactions and anonymized analytics to improve our services. We only collect data that is necessary for providing our الصحة companion services. You have full control over what information you provide.",
  "privacySectionDataStorage": "2. Data Storage & Encryption",
  "privacyDataStorageBody": "Your data is stored using industry-leading security measures:\n\n• Encryption at Rest: All data stored in our databases is encrypted using AES-256 encryption.\n• Encryption in Transit: All data transmitted between your device and our servers uses TLS 1.3 encryption.\n• Health Passport: Your health passport data is encrypted with a unique key derived from your credentials.\n• رمز QR Sharing: Shared health data via QR codes is encrypted and time-limited.\n• Infrastructure: Our servers are hosted in SOC 2 Type II certified data centers with 24/7 monitoring.\n\nWe do not store payment card information. All payment processing is handled by certified third-party providers.",
  "privacySectionGdpr": "3. GDPR Compliance",
  "privacyGdprBody": "{appName} is fully compliant with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR): • Lawful Basis: We process your data based on your explicit consent and contractual necessity. • Data Minimization: We only collect and process data that is strictly necessary. • Purpose Limitation: Your data is used only for the purposes for which it was collected. • Right to Access: You can request a complete copy of your personal data at any tالوقت • Right to Rectification: You can update or correct your data through the app sالإعدادات • Right to Erasure: You can request complete deletion of your account and data. • Right to Portability: You can تصدير your data in a machine-readable format. • Data Processing Agreements: الكل third-party processors have signed DPAs. • Cross-Border Transfers: Data is processed within the EU/EEA unless explicit consent is given otherwise.",
  "privacySectionYourRights": "4. Your Rights",
  "privacyRightsBody": "You have the following rights regarding your data: • Access: View الكل your personal and الصحة data within the app or request a data eتصدير • Correction: تعديل your الملف الشخصي information at any الوقت through تعديل Pالملف الشخصي • Deletion: Request account deletion through الإعدادات > Data & الخصوصية > حذف Account. • Restriction: Limit how certain data is processed by adjusting your notification and sharing preferences. • Objection: Object to specific data processing activities by contacting our Data Protection Officer. • Withdrawal of Consent: You may withdraw consent at any الوقت without affecting the lawfulness of prior processing. To exercise any of these rights, contact us at privacy@vitalseker.com or through the in-app الدعم feature.",
  "privacySectionContactUs": "5. Contact Us",
  "privacyContactBody": "If you have any questions or concerns حول this الخصوصية Policy or our data practices, please contact us: • Eالبريد الإلكتروني privacy@vitalseker.com • Sالدعم support@vitalseker.com • Data Protection Officer: dpo@vitalseker.com • Address: {producer}, Data Protection Office We aim to respond to الكل privacy-related inquiries within 30 days.",
